{
  "stem": "3631.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And some high-- the quartermaster, some high officers of the civilian army, not the SS army, the other army, moved in there, and we-- they let us stay there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We kept a very, very low profile.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We, we, we got out of the window so we didn't have to go through the, through the, through the hall, and so we managed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We stayed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And at that time, we were protected a little bit by, by the fact there was always a German guard outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So the-- like the Germans who made raids into, into, into houses where Jewish people lived, did not come in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we-- again, it was one of the things that we were lucky for awhile.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a occupation by a hostile force.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, there was a curfew at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to get up at 1 o'clock at night to stand in line for bread in the morning, until somebody in the morning-- if you got something, you were lucky.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was, it was winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the winters in Poland got very cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, the Jews, as of December 1, '39, we had to wear a Levite armband with a, with a Star of David.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Jews were picked up from the street by German army and SS groups who threw them onto the truck if they need workers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They picked, just picked them up from the street and had to put them on their truck and had to take them to work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nobody knew where they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And most of them came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of them, they never came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them were beaten up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was a steady thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
